<section class="frontpage">
    <div class="header-background ">
        <div class="row top-banner">
            <div class="small-12 large-5 columns">
                <div class="background-header-pattern">
                    <div data-lazy-image data-src="/static/images/svg/header-background-pattern-rez.svg" data-as-background=".background-header-pattern"></div>
                    <h1 class="wait-for-font">
                        <strong>JavaScript Spreadsheet</strong><br/>
                        <span>Most popular UI component for web apps</span>
                    </h1>
                    <h2 class="wait-for-font">
                        A fast, secure, and reliable solution.<br/>
                        Available for React, Angular and Vue.
                    </h2>
                    <a href="/features.html" class="btn size-large bg-white text-blue shadow hover-moveup">Learn
                        more</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 large-5 columns">
                <div data-lazy-image data-src="/static/images/svg/header-laptop.svg" data-class-name="header-laptop" style="width: 720px; height: 720px;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="stripe-gray">
        <%- partial("_partials/_brands_frontpage") %>
    </div>

    <div class="highlights">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <h2>
                    <hr/>
                    Spreadsheet experience
                </h2>
                <p>Handsontable provides a spreadsheet experience you are already familiar with.
                    Start working effectively from day one.</p>
                <div class="benefits-testimonial">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="small-2 columns">
                            <div data-lazy-image data-src="<%= img_path %>template/ModCustomers/nuxeo/nuxeo-avatar.png" style="width: 31px; height: 31px;"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="small-10 columns">
                            <p>„Handsontable had the greatest documentation, and an impressive feature set”</p>
                            <p>Alain Escaffre, VP at Nuxeo</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center artwork">
                <svg class="svg">
                    <use xlink:href="#spreadsheet-experience"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center artwork">
                <svg class="svg">
                    <use xlink:href="#powerful-features"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <h2>
                    <hr/>
                    Created for developers
                </h2>
                <p>Handsontable is designed to be easy to implement, and as customizable as possible.
                    It includes a comprehensive API, useful tutorials, and both community and commercial support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <h2>
                    <hr/>
                    High performance
                </h2>
                <p>You can finally work with large volumes of data without worrying about performance issues.
                    Large companies and startups use Handsontable to build their business critical applications.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center artwork">
                <svg class="svg">
                    <use xlink:href="#powerful-experience"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="testimony stripe-gray">
        <div class="row">
            <h2 class="text-center size-large">What our customers say<br/>
                <span>Diverse industries benefit from using Handsontable in their business apps</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <div class="bubble">
                    <div class="quote">„We recommend Handsontable without hesitation, especially if the project
                        requires the handling of large amounts of data.”
                        <div class="triangle"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefits-testimonial">
                        <div class="row large-collapse">
                            <div class="small-3 columns text-center">
                                <div data-lazy-image data-src="<%= img_path %>template/ModCustomers/socialpoint/socialpoint-avatar42x42.png" data-alt="Julio de la Calle" style="width: 42px; height: 42px;"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="small-9 columns">
                                <p>Julio de la Calle</p>
                                <p>JS Architect at Social Point</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <div class="bubble">
                    <div class="quote">„Handsontable was a perfect fit because it looks and feels just like Excel, a
                        tool teachers are already familiar with.”
                        <div class="triangle"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefits-testimonial">
                        <div class="row large-collapse">
                            <div class="small-3 columns text-center">
                                <div data-lazy-image data-src="<%= img_path %>template/ModCustomers/akindi/akindi-avatar42x42.png" data-alt="David Wolever" style="width: 42px; height: 42px;"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="small-9 columns">
                                <p>David Wolever</p>
                                <p>CTO at Akindi</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <div class="bubble">
                    <div class="quote">„We've found Handsontable to be a good partner:
                        easy to work with and attentive to the specifications of our product.”
                        <div class="triangle"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="benefits-testimonial">
                        <div class="row large-collapse">
                            <div class="small-3 columns text-center">
                                <div data-lazy-image data-src="<%= img_path %>template/ModCustomers/trackingfirst/trackingfirst-avatar42x42.png" data-alt="Craig Scribner" style="width: 42px; height: 42px;"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="small-9 columns">
                                <p>Craig Scribner</p>
                                <p>CEO at Tracking First</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row open-source">
        <h2 class="text-center size-large">Open source at heart<br/>
            <span>A community that actively contribute to the development of Handsontable</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center">
            <div class="chart">
                <div class="cloud issues">
                    <strong data-bind="closedIssuesCount">-</strong>
                    <span>closed issues</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cloud commits">
                    <strong data-bind="commitsCount">-</strong>
                    <span>commits</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cloud stars">
                    <strong data-bind="starsCount">-</strong>
                    <span>stars</span>
                </div>
                <div data-lazy-image data-src="/static/images/svg/social-diagram.png" data-alt="GitHub statistics" style="max-width: 441px; height: 420px;"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="small-12 medium-5 columns">
            <p><strong>Handsontable</strong> was first published on GitHub in 2012 and has since grown in popularity
                among developers interested in enriching their apps with spreadsheet capabilities.</p>
            <p>We are proud to continue this work by providing various companies with a powerful
                and secure spreadsheet component.
            </p>
            <a href="/download.html">Go to download</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row get-started">
        <h2 class="text-center size-large">Get started now<br/>
            <span>Build and launch your next business application with Handsontable</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="large-6 columns large-centered text-center">
            <a href="/download.html" class="btn size-large bg-green bg-lighten hover-moveup text-white shadow">Download</a>
            <a href="/features.html"
               class="btn size-large bg-blue bg-lighten hover-moveup text-white shadow">See features</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>